OL,3,CSwollen ankles and legs: lesser known
OL,4,Cheart failure symptoms to watch out for
OL,6,FGoing to see a doctor for a routine
OL,7,Fcheck-up can be a lifesaver when it
OL,8,Fcomes to spotting signs of potentially
OL,9,Ffatal cardiovascular problems,
OL,10,Faccording to one Channel Islander who
OL,11,Fnearly died of heart failure.
OL,13,FArtur Rodrigues, 51, was diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith the condition shortly after
OL,15,Fvisiting his GP in Jersey when he
OL,16,Fsuddenly felt extremely tired.
OL,18,FAfter further tests, he was taken to
OL,19,Fhospital and eventually transferred to
OL,20,Fthe UK for treatment and after being
OL,21,Fseriously ill, has fully recovered.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778436665
OL,3,CSwollen ankles and legs: lesser known
OL,4,Cheart failure symptoms to watch out for
OL,6,FArtur is now urging anyone who does
OL,7,Fnot feel right to seek medical advice
OL,8,Fas soon as they can.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News about his
OL,11,Fexperience, Artur said: "I was a
OL,12,Flittle bit worried because I didn't
OL,13,Fhave family here and I didn't know
OL,14,Fanything about they were going to take
OL,15,Fcare of me but they did an excellent
OL,16,Fjob."
OL,18,FHe added: "If you feel anything (that
OL,19,Fdoes not feel right), just go to the
OL,20,FGP. Don't be scared because it can
OL,21,Fsave your life. It saved my life.
OL,26,@zD@apm{D@Tpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
