OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778436665
OL,3,CSwollen ankles and legs: lesser known
OL,4,Cheart failure symptoms to watch out for
OL,6,F"If I'd waited one week longer, I
OL,7,Fthink I would've passed away, believe
OL,8,Fme."
OL,10,FHeart disease is one of the leading
OL,11,Fcauses of deaths in the Channel
OL,12,FIslands and with the number of people
OL,13,Fwith cardiovascular problems in Jersey
OL,14,Falone expected to grow by 43% by 2043,
OL,15,Fhealth experts say it is more
OL,16,Fimportant than ever that islanders are
OL,17,Faware of some of the symptoms to look
OL,18,Fout for.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778436665
OL,3,CSwollen ankles and legs: lesser known
OL,4,Cheart failure symptoms to watch out for
OL,6,FSinead O'Driscoll, Advanced Clinical
OL,7,FPractitioner at Jersey General
OL,8,FHospital, said: "Some people feel
OL,9,Fextremely tired, fatigued, they can
OL,10,Fget breathless and it can be over
OL,11,Fprolonged periods of time or it could
OL,12,Fbe quite sudden, or it can also
OL,13,Fdevelop in the sense that people might
OL,14,Fhave progressive leg swelling, fluid
OL,15,Fon their lungs.
OL,17,F"You never know when you're going to
OL,18,Fget diagnosed. We have lots of people
OL,19,Fin their 30s and 40s who have been
OL,20,Fadmitted with heart failure."
OL,26,@nD@Drr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778436665
OL,3,CSwollen ankles and legs: lesser known
OL,4,Cheart failure symptoms to watch out for
OL,6,FSinead adds that regular exercise,
OL,7,Fhaving a healthy diet, as well as
OL,8,Favoiding smoking and excessive
OL,9,Fdrinking, can help control blood
OL,10,Fpressure which is pivotal in reducing
OL,11,Fthe risk of heart disease.
OL,13,FA series of pop-up clinics were held
OL,14,Fin the hospital and in the Central
OL,15,FMarket last week which gave members of
OL,16,Fthe public chance to have some routine
OL,17,Fheart tests for free.
OL,26,@nD@Drr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1778436665
OL,3,CSwollen ankles and legs: lesser known
OL,4,Cheart failure symptoms to watch out for
OL,6,FAnd of the 266 islanders who attended
OL,7,Fthe clinics, 100 were identified as
OL,8,Fhaving high blood pressure and were
OL,9,Fadvised to visit their GP and one case
OL,10,Fof atrial fibrillation - a rapid,
OL,11,Firregular heartbeat - was spotted,
OL,12,Fleading to that individual being
OL,13,Fadvised to book an appointment with
OL,14,Ftheir doctor as a matter or urgency.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
